data.description: Charming Log Home located in Dammeron Valley. Breathtaking views of surrounding valley and mountains. Home features large kitchen with plenty of counter and storage space, Spacious living room with lots of windows and fireplace. Master Bedroom features vaulted ceilings ad large walk in closet. Quality finish work throughout! Home is heated with high efficiency pellet stove and cooled with commercial grade swamp cooler. Home is situated on .63 acre with plenty of room for the toys or potential garage/shop. Backyard is fenced for animal and boasts 3 large sheds for storage.
